name: Jumping Jack Semi-Final Version
description: This is my Semi-Final Version of the Jumping Jack game, there is still a lot more I want to do with it and I think just a tiny bit of copy right music in the music menu, I'm not 100% sure though, and once I get my final version up all of that stuff should be fixed, but the level design is almost finished and the boss battle I created called Mecha-Godzilla and of course Ultra Instinct Shaggy joins forces with him as he's known as Mecha Shaggy. I based him off of the meem.
